name: Journal of Computational Geometry
summary:
The Journal of Computational Geometry (JoCG) is an open access mathematics journal that was established in 2010. It covers research in all aspects of computational geometry. All its papers are published free of charge to both authors and readers, and are made freely available through a Creative Commons Attribution license. The current editors-in-chief are Kenneth L.
